  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:0",
      "text": "Features tab 可用于启用 RenderMan renderer 的特殊 features，例如 renderer type、OCIO、Motion Blur 等。",
      "ascii_letters": 62,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:1",
      "text": "Renderer",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:2",
      "text": "定义场景使用的 RenderMan renderer。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:4",
      "text": "：使用 RIS render 场景。这是 CPU-only renderer。",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:6",
      "text": "使用 XPU render 场景。这是 CPU + GPU hybrid renderer。",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:7",
      "text": "XPU Mode - CPU",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:8",
      "text": "：使用 XPU render，但只使用 CPU。",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:9",
      "text": "XPU Mode - GPU",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:10",
      "text": "：使用 XPU render，但只使用 GPU。",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:11",
      "text": "Motion Blur",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:13",
      "text": "motion blur",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:15",
      "text": "Motion Blur:",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:16",
      "text": "启用 motion blur 会让移动 objects 沿其运动 path 产生 blur，以防止 temporal aliasing 和 strobing。使用 motion blur 时，应增加 pixel samples 的数量（Sampling tab 中的 max samples），并预期 rendering times 会更长。",
      "ascii_letters": 106,
      "cjk_chars": 33
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:18",
      "text": "：完整 render 且准确的 motion blur",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:20",
      "text": "：会计算 motion vectors，但 motion blur 此时",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:22",
      "text": "被 render；在输出 dPdtime 和 dPdcameratime 等 AOVs 后用于 post processes 时很有用。",
      "ascii_letters": 43,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:23",
      "text": "Camera Blur:",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:25",
      "text": "Shutter Angle:",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:26",
      "text": "Shutter Angle",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:28",
      "text": "Shutter Opening:",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:30",
      "text": "Shutter Opening",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:33",
      "text": "。它们是 shutter interval 的 fractions，可用于调整 shutter 打开和关闭所需时间。从 0 到",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 20
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:36",
      "text": "Shutter Timing:",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:37",
      "text": "Shutter Timing",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:39",
      "text": "OpenColorIO",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:40",
      "text": "Configuration",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:42",
      "text": "：使用系统 environment variable 定义的 color space",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:44",
      "text": "Scene Linear 被定义为 scene-wide color space",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:46",
      "text": "：使用 RenderMan 24 随附的 ACES 1.2 color space",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:48",
      "text": "：允许指定 custom color space file",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:49",
      "text": "Interactive Denoiser",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:50",
      "text": "此 Interactive Denoiser 在 Maya viewport 中启用，并提供 RenderMan",
      "ascii_letters": 40,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:51",
      "text": "Machine Learning Denoiser",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:53",
      "text": "Cheap First Pass",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:55",
      "text": "Min Samples",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:56",
      "text": "：Denoiser 首次运行前所需的最低 average samples 数。",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:57",
      "text": "Interval",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:58",
      "text": "：Denoise 运行之间的 time interval，单位为 seconds。",
      "ascii_letters": 26,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "c2987eac15:59",
      "text": "Stylized Looks",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
